{"title":"2022 Kona Shonky Dirt Jump and Pump Track Bike gets new… paint?","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/22/2022-kona-shonky-dirt-jump-and-pump-track-bike-gets-new-paint/","date":1624345193000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>The 2022 Kona Shonky Dirt Jump and Pump Track Bike remains largely unchanged for this model year. The geometry and parts specification are exactly the same… the only thing that has changed is the color. <em>So what?</em></p><figure id=\"attachment_262153\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-262153\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120136/CarlosLaangelaan-Kona-Shonky-2022.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120136/CarlosLaangelaan-Kona-Shonky-2022.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x324/rscb18/ng:webp/ngcb18\" alt=\"carlos laangelaan kona shonky bicycle nightmares\" width=\"1200\" height=\"804\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120136/CarlosLaangelaan-Kona-Shonky-2022.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120136/CarlosLaangelaan-Kona-Shonky-2022-297x199.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120136/CarlosLaangelaan-Kona-Shonky-2022-800x536.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120136/CarlosLaangelaan-Kona-Shonky-2022-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120136/CarlosLaangelaan-Kona-Shonky-2022-768x515.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120136/