ttps://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120136/CarlosLaangelaan-Kona-Shonky-2022-627x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 627w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-262153\">Credit: Hector Saura of Bicycle Nightmares</figcaption></figure><p>OK, OK, bear with… Kona have however, provided us with a rather lovely video of their gravity team rider Carlos Langelaan putting the Shonky through its paces. It is beautifully shot by Hector Saura of Bicycle Nightmares, allowing us to appreciate the full extent of Carlos’ dirt jump prowess.</p><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"vimeo-player\" data-ezsrc=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/521779012\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p><p>The Kona Shonky steel dirt jump bike gets a fresh paint job for 2022. And, nothing more. If last year’s Gloss Champagne frame paint was the only thing stopping you from emptying your pockets, perhaps this year’s pastel coral green will be enough to tip you over the edge… maybe.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem.jpg\" alt=\"2022 kona shonky coral green\" width=\"1200\" height=\"700\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-297x173.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-800x467.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-120x70.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-768x448.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-696x406.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-1068x623.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-720x420.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-297x173.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-800x467.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-120x70.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-768x448.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-696x406.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-1068x623.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120123/2022-kona-shonky-complete-bike-greem-720x420.jpg 720w\"></a></p><p>Regardless of the paint job, there’s no denying this is a beautiful steel frame dirt jump bike. The chromoly butted frame features head tube gussets, a machined yoke and modular dropouts, giving it a little more class than your average aluminium frame DJ bike.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120159/kona-shonky-steel-frame-dj-bike-headtube-gussets.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120159/kona-shonky-steel-frame-dj-bike-headtube-gussets.jpg\" alt=\"kona shonky gusseted steel frame dirt jump bike 26&quot; wheels\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120159/kona-shonky-steel-frame-dj-bike-headtube-gussets.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120159/kona-shonky-steel-frame-dj-bike-headtube-gussets-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120159/kona-shonky-steel-frame-dj-bike-headtube-gussets-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120159/kona-shonky-steel-frame-dj-bike-headtube-gussets-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120159/kona-shonky-steel-frame-dj-bike-headtube-gussets-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/17120159/kona-shonky-steel-frame-dj-bike-headtube-gussets-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.a